Import et mise en forme des donnes

countries <- st_read("world/data/geom/countries.gpkg")
graticule <- st_read("world/data/geom/graticule.gpkg")
bbox <- st_read("world/data/geom/bbox.gpkg")
migr <- read.csv("world/data/fij/migr2019_T.csv")

crs <- "+proj=aeqd +lat_0=90 +lon_0=50 +x_0=0 +y_0=0 +datum=WGS84 +units=m +no_defs "
countries <- st_transform(x = countries, crs = crs)
graticule <- st_transform(x = graticule, crs = crs)
bbox <- st_transform(x = bbox, crs = crs)
land <- st_union(countries)

Template cartographique

  credit = "Franoise Bahoken & Nicolas Lambert, 2021\nSource: United Nations, Department of Economic and Social Affairs, Population Division (2019)"
  theme = mf_theme(x = "default", bg = "white", tab = FALSE, pos = "center", line = 3,
                   inner = TRUE, fg = "#9F2042", mar = c(0,0, 0, 0), cex = 1.5)
  title = "Map Template"
  file = "maps/template.png"
    mf_export(
    countries,
    export = "png",
    width = 1000,
    height = 1000,
    filename = file,
    res = 96,
    theme = theme
  )
  mf_map(bbox, col = "#d5ebf2",border = NA, lwd = 0.5, add = TRUE)
  mf_map(graticule, col = "white", lwd = 0.5, add = TRUE)
  mf_map(countries, col = "#baaba2",border = "white", lwd = 0.5, add = TRUE)
  mf_map(land, col = NA,border = "#607c9e", lwd = 1, add = TRUE)
  mf_credits(
    txt = credit,
    pos = "bottomright",
    col = "#1a2640",
    cex = 0.7,
    font = 3,
    bg = NA
  )
  mf_title(title)
  dev.off()

Leffet Spaghetti

  title = "L'effet Spaghetti"
  file = "maps/spaghetti.png"
  
  mf_export(
    countries,
    export = "png",
    width = 1000,
    height = 1000,
    filename = file,
    res = 96,
    theme = theme
  )
  mf_map(bbox, col = "#d5ebf2",border = NA, lwd = 0.5, add = TRUE)
  mf_map(graticule, col = "white", lwd = 0.5, add = TRUE)
  mf_map(countries, col = "#baaba2",border = "white", lwd = 0.5, add = TRUE)
  mf_map(links, col = "#9F204270", lwd = 1, add=TRUE)
    mf_map(land, col = NA,border = "white", lwd = 0.5, add = TRUE)

    txt = credit,
